  "2026-06-06T16:31:55.721Z",codex-agent,"Added explicit in-repo tracking constants for the upstream fix watch (dependency=@toon-format/toon, affected_versions<=2.3.0, upstream_pr=https://github.com/toon-format/toon/pull/314, removal_condition text) and guard tests that (1) ensure quoted-scalar bracket recovery still works while preserving array-header semantics and (2) assert upstream linkage remains documented for future removal. Verification: node scripts/run-tests.mjs test -- tests/unit/toon-decode.spec.ts."
